<h1><strong>Come meet us at OpenStack Booth D21 - there's lots&nbsp;going on.</strong></h1>

<p>We have officially landed in lovely Boston to a beautiful day, and are getting excited about packed OpenStack starting tomorrow.</p>
<p><img style="float: left; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px;" src="/img/boston.jpeg" alt="" width="163" height="165" /></p>
<h2><strong>Where to find us and what to do...</strong></h2>
<p>Cloudify is excited to be able to be a part of the excellent Open Source Day initiative, and will be having our very own <a href="https://www.openstack.org/summit/boston-2017/summit-schedule/#track=150" target="_blank">track</a>&nbsp;located at the <strong>Sheraton Boston Hotel - 2nd Floor - Back Bay Ballroom B.</strong></p>
<p>There are a lot of exciting talks on the agenda - Cloudify Architecture, Apache ARIA, Introducing ONAP, Open vCPE and more. &nbsp;Join us and be sure to pick up a swag pack.</p>

  <hr>
<span class="pullquote-left">
