<hr>
<h3><strong>Survey Says...</strong></h3>
<p>We will also be giving fun stuff out to those who fill out <strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfEaudLnTWgy4qc1VB6ivj9I0YxRIE0wcI7RN_kaNQxm3sBKw/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1" target="_blank">State of Cloud Orchestration survey</a></strong>. &nbsp;You can fill it out in advance, and stop by booth D21 to pick up your swag.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h3><strong>#NERFCHALLENGE</strong></h3>
<p><img style="float: right; margin-right: 10px; margin-left: 10px;" src="/img/nerf.jpeg" alt="" width="163" height="165" /></p>
<p>It's no secret that we at Cloudify like to have a bit of fun - come to our booth and take the nerd...err Nerf Challenge - #GETCLOUDIFY #GETNERF. Tweet it and reserve your Nerf early.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<h2><strong>Talks and other Blah Blah...</strong></h2>
<p>We have two excellent talks and a demo theater session you won't want to miss.</p>
<ul>
<li>Join DeWayne Filppi&nbsp;at the Marketplace Demo Theater presenting:&nbsp;<em><strong>Cloudify - Hybrid Orchestration: Automation Across and Between Heterogenous Platforms</strong></em>, Monday, May 8, 1:55PM</li>
<li>Join Arthur Berezin for his talk&nbsp;<em><strong>How Cloud Native VNFs on OpenStack will Change the Telecom Industry,&nbsp;</strong></em><a class="search-link" href="https://www.openstack.org/summit/boston-2017/venues/#room=257">Hynes Convention Center - Level Three - MR 312</a>, Tuesday May 9, 11:15AM</li>
<li>Join me (Sharone Zitzman) for an excellent panel discussion on the&nbsp;<em><strong>Amazon Effect on Open Source Cloud Business Models</strong></em>,&nbsp;<a class="search-link" href="https://www.openstack.org/summit/boston-2017/venues/#room=257">Hynes Convention Center - Level Three - MR 312</a>, Wednesday May 10, 3:30PM</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>If you want to meet up with us you can tweet to us at <a href="http://www.twitter.com/cloudifysource" target="_blank">@cloudifysource</a>, use the hashtag #getcloudify with #openstack and get swag.</p>
